The Seeing Is Not Sharing (SINS) Binary Common-Ground Judgment Dataset is
derived from chnln/grounded-misunderstandings-in-maptask (GMMT), distributed
under CC BY 4.0. The local reconstruction helper adapts the public GMMT
transcript reconstruction logic while requiring users to supply their own
authorised MapTask material.

This release does not redistribute MapTask dialogue context, maps, images,
OCR, image-derived text, or source-transcript files. Reconstructed contexts
are not part of the SINS distribution.
